{"tid":661951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬來西亞移民局證實禁止納吉夫婦出境","createTime":"2018-05-12T04:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T06:56:52.000Z","uid":41404,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"48ce64bd457570a107d543d8a1af0469ad6a6527","tid":661951,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:15:52.000Z","msg":"大馬移民局今早約11時17分在社交媒體發表聲明，證實將前首相納吉和夫人羅斯瑪列入黑名單，禁止他們出境。<br />\n<br />\n移民局在短時間內，二度將納吉夫婦列入旅遊權黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;華爾街日報&rdquo;今日凌晨爆料，指馬哈迪政府下令移民局，將納吉夫婦列入黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orientaldaily.com.my/s/242962#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fs%2F242962%23&d=3juTG67kHkovhAVMyh4CYv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=d3fd03c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orientaldaily.com.my/s/242962#</a>"},{"pid":"99f80543c2ee2314ffced729fdd9d7ac059f1e39","tid":661951,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:18:41.000Z","msg":"花生"},{"pid":"97df15be336f8c2b60be4675098efa8e3ea9025b","tid":661951,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:24:09.000Z","msg":"Datuk Seri Najib Tun Razak said he will remain in Malaysia with his family due to the Immigration Department's blacklist against him from leaving the country.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I have been informed that the Immigration Department of Malaysia is not allowing my family and me to go out of the country.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I will respect the decision and will remain in the country with my family,&quot; said the former Prime Minister.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2018/05/12/najib-confirms-immigration-blacklist\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestar.com.my%2Fnews%2Fnation%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2Fnajib-confirms-immigration-blacklist&d=3juTG67kHkovhAVMyh4CYv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c3659a41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestar.com.